User Stories: (We are Developers)
­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­­
1. user wants to see the menu screen and be able to post a ride request so that people can be
connected to share rides. 5 days
2. User wants to see a home screen that displays available posts and can create a post so that
people can see where the user wants to go. 1 week
3. User wants to be able to click on the post and the post will expand with information so that
people can pick rides good for them. 4 days
4.User wants a group chat for people in the same group so that people in the same group can
communicate details about the ride. 3 days ­ low priority
5. User would like a map view so that people can know where their destination is on a map.
(Low priority) 1 week
6. User wants a group page so that people in the same group can be connected. ­ want to be
able to contact people in the car 1 week
7. Users wants to set group restrictions so that people can’t join every group. 3 days
8. User wants drivers to enter their information for them to post a ride so that people will be
discouraged from making fake rides 2 days
9. User wants the title to be just source to destination and time so that the posts are informative
and you don’t have to look hard to find information. 3 days
10. User wants a comment box (Block of text) for more information when the post is selected so
that users can get more information about rides. 2 days
11. User would like the two feeds separated by color but in the same location so that all rides
can be seen together and that they are easily identified if they are uber rides or one with a
driver. 3 days
12. User wants a group page to see all of the groups you’ve been added to.so that users can
keep track of their rides. 2 days
13. User wants people to be able to leave their groups so that they can cancel their rides as
needed. 3 days
14. User would like priority to be determined by departure time so that more recent rides will be
seen first. 2 days
15. User would like the post creator’s Name, email, phone number, facebook, etc. so that the
user can be easily contacted. 4 days
